title: Batman 999
data:
Batman (999) 
 Based on the Character created by Bob Kane. 
 EXT. CITYSCAPE - NIGHT 
 Gotham City.  The City of Tomorrow:  stark angles, creeping shadows, dense, crowded, as if hell had erupted through the sidewalks.  A dangling fat moon shines overhead. 
 At the opposite corner of the roof, some fifteen yards away... at the end of a line, a STRANGE BLACK SILHOUETTE is dropping slowly, implacably, into frame...
